set AppleScript's text item delimiters to linefeed try tell application "Finder" set theSelectionPathList to selection if length of theSelectionPathList = 0 then return "" repeat with theItem in theSelectionPathList set contents of theItem to POSIX path of (theItem as text) end repeat end tell return theSelectionPathList as text on error return ""
end try
